    dc:date "2012" ;
    dc:title "A new species of the Bokermannohyla circumdata group (Anura: Hylidae) from southeastern Brazil, with bioacoustic data on seven species of the genus" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214865>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214866> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214865>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Adult specimens of Bokermannohyla napolii sp. nov. in life. Specimens from the Estação de Pesquisa e Desenvolvimento Ambiental Galheiro (EPDA-Galheiro), Municipality of Perdizes, State of Minas Gerais, Brazil. Upper, holotype UFMG 3333; Lower, female paratopotype ZUEC 16609." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214865/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214866>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Ventral view of hands of adult male specimens of Bokermannohyla napolii sp. nov. (left: ZUEC 16610) and B. luctuosa (right: AAG-UFU 0473). The arrows point to the divided tubercles of fingers III and IV in B. napolii sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214866/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

